Title:
This was the worse seating layout I ever experienced on a long flight {21 hrs.}
The airbus seating allowed the passenger in front of you to put their seat all the way back, allowing inches only to move. To get out of your seat was a chore and very uncomfortable. The seat padding was insufficient for the length of the flight. I had the vegetarian entrée unappetizing in looks and quality.
I was overjoyed to get out of the jet no more airbus flights if I can help it. Note the staff was very pleasant sorry they have to endure these flights
